''' 斩首视频'''是一种充分展示人质被[[斩首|斩首]]过程的宣传视频。<ref>{{cite news|last=Stannard|first=Matthew B.|url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?file=/c/a/2004/05/13/MNG6E6KL791.DTL|title=Beheading video seen as war tactic|work=[[San_Francisco_Chronicle|San Francisco Chronicle]]|date=May 13, 2004|accessdate=November 23, 2010|archive-date=2012-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120208095429/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?file=%2Fc%2Fa%2F2004%2F05%2F13%2FMNG6E6KL791.DTL|dead-url=no}}</ref>这种视频在2004年被伊斯兰主义激进分子[[阿布·穆萨布·扎卡维|阿布·穆萨布·扎卡维]]所推广，并引起了伊斯兰学者的争论。一些伊斯兰学者公开指责这种视频违反了伊斯兰教法；[[基地组织|基地组织]]却不认同这一看法。无论如何，斩首视频在一些伊斯兰恐怖组织中流行开来，例如[[伊拉克和沙姆伊斯兰国|伊拉克和沙姆伊斯兰国]]。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/posteverything/wp/2014/08/22/even-al-qaeda-denounced-beheading-videos-why-the-islamic-state-brought-them-back/|title=Even al-Qaeda denounced beheading videos. Why the Islamic State brought them back.|last=Bloom|first=Mia|authorlink=Mia Bloom|work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|date=August 22, 2014|accessdate=August 23, 2014|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115090657/https://www.washingtonpost.com/posteverything/wp/2014/08/22/even-al-qaeda-denounced-beheading-videos-why-the-islamic-state-brought-them-back/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在这些视频中所展示的斩首通常不表现为“传统”的方法——用[[剑|剑]]或[[斧|斧]]迅速地将受害者头部砍下，而是在受害者存活之际用[[小刀|小刀]]缓慢地[[割|割]]或[[锯|锯]]被害者的颈部直到头部与身体分离。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://pando.com/2014/09/03/the-war-nerd-the-long-twisted-history-of-beheadings-as-propaganda/|title=The long, twisted history of beheadings as propaganda|last=Brecher|first=Gary|publisher=[[PandoDaily|PandoDaily]]|date=September 3, 2014|accessdate=2015-04-26|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127211209/https://pando.com/2014/09/03/the-war-nerd-the-long-twisted-history-of-beheadings-as-propaganda/|dead-url=no}}</ref>所以，伊斯兰主义者的“斩首”确切地说应该是“割头”。

早期的这类视频是模糊而简单的，不过根据《[[芝加哥太阳报|芝加哥太阳报]]》的说法，“（斩首视频）变得越来越复杂，使用动画图形编辑技术显然旨在修饰音频使受害者的最后时刻更加令人不安。”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-1549085.html|title=Terrorists sense power in beheading videos|last=Shrader|first=Katherine Pfleger|work=[[Chicago_Sun-Times|Chicago Sun-Times]]|date=September 29, 2004|accessdate=August 23, 2014|subscription=yes|via=[[Highbeam_Research|Highbeam Research]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140921194733/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-1549085.html|archive-date=2014-09-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>这些视频经常被恐怖分子上传到[[万维网|万维网]]，然后被各种网络载体所讨论和传播，<ref>{{cite news|last1=Palmer|first1=Ewan|title=James Foley: Police Warn Watching Beheading Video Is A 'Terrorist Offence'|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/james-foley-police-warn-watching-beheading-video-terrorist-offence-1461974|accessdate=23 August 2014|publisher=[[International_Business_Times|International Business Times]]|date=August 20, 2014|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126180023/https://www.ibtimes.co.uk/james-foley-police-warn-watching-beheading-video-terrorist-offence-1461974|dead-url=no}}</ref>如[[博客|博客]]、{{le|惊悚网站|Shock sites}}和传统新闻媒体。一个墨西哥贩毒集团将一段热门的斩首视频发布到了[[Facebook|Facebook]]上，{{le|家庭在线安全研究所|Family Online Safety Institute}}请求将它删除。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-347573697.html|title=Facebook Graphic Content Woes: When Are Beheading Videos Okay?|last=Karis|first=Hustad|work=[[The_Christian_Science_Monitor|The Christian Science Monitor]]|date=October 31, 2013|accessdate=August 23, 2014|subscription=yes|via=[[Highbeam_Research|Highbeam Research]]|archivedate=2014-09-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140921200611/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-347573697.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 最初Facebook拒绝了这一请求，<ref name=ibt>{{cite news|last1=Su|first1=Reissa|title=Beheaded Woman in Viral Video on Facebook 'Unknown,' Authorities Not Investigating (VIDEO)|url=http://au.ibtimes.com/articles/519273/20131104/beheaded-woman-facebook-mexico-drug-cartel-narco.htm#.VFShQNapdKp|accessdate=1 November 2014|publisher=International Business Times|date=4 November 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141031161337/http://au.ibtimes.com/articles/519273/20131104/beheaded-woman-facebook-mexico-drug-cartel-narco.htm#.VFShQNapdKp|archivedate=2014年10月31日}}</ref>而后保持了这一决定，<ref name=bbcgrant>{{cite news|last1=Grant|first1=Willl|title=Facebook beheading video: Who was Mexico's Jane Doe?|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/magazine-24772724|accessdate=1 November 2014|publisher=BBC News Online|date=3 November 2013|archive-date=2021-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127093640/https://www.bbc.com/news/magazine-24772724|dead-url=no}}</ref>后来澄清了他们的政策，表示斩首视频只被允许以让用户“谴责”这类行为的预期态度发布。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/10/21/net-us-facebook-violence-idUSBRE99K14020131021|title=Gory videos OK when posted for users to 'condemn': Facebook|last=Oreskovic|first=Alexei|work=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|date=October 21, 2013|accessdate=August 23, 2014|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924190109/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/10/21/net-us-facebook-violence-idUSBRE99K14020131021|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

