一段由本杰明·范德福德、罗比特·马丁和劳里·柯克纳制作的伪造的斩首视频在2004年被美国媒体广泛关注。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Guthrie|first1=Julian|last2=Wallace|first2=Bill|title=Web hoax fools news services|url=http://www.sfgate.com/news/article/Web-hoax-fools-news-services-S-F-man-fakes-2702773.php|accessdate=October 3, 2014|publisher=San Francisco Chronicle|date=August 8, 2004|archive-date=2021-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210223205242/https://www.sfgate.com/news/article/Web-hoax-fools-news-services-S-F-man-fakes-2702773.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>该视频使用了{{le|认主独一圣战组织|Jama'at al-Tawhid wal-Jihad}}的标志，但是没有该组织的旗帜。<ref>{{cite news|title='Beheaded hostage' video exposed as hoax|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-313201/Beheaded-hostage-video-exposed-hoax.html|accessdate=October 3, 2014|publisher=Daily Mail|date=August 7, 2014|archive-date=2020-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200329171935/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-313201/Beheaded-hostage-video-exposed-hoax.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>它被制作出来用以范德福德的本地竞选。<ref>{{cite news|title=Man fakes own decapitation in video|url=http://www.theage.com.au/articles/2004/08/08/1091903424028.html?from=storylhs|accessdate=October 3, 2014|publisher=The Age|date=August 8, 2004|archive-date=2015-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150318120719/http://www.theage.com.au/articles/2004/08/08/1091903424028.html?from=storylhs|dead-url=no}}</ref>他当时正在谋取{{le|马特·冈萨雷斯|Matt Gonzalez}}在旧金山{{le|监事会（美国中西部及东部各州）|Board of Supervisors}}的席位。<ref>{{cite news|last1=DiMassa|first1=Cara Mia|last2=Hollis|first2=Robert|title=Region & State Man Fakes Own Beheading Video|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2004/aug/08/local/me-video8|accessdate=October 3, 2014|publisher=Los Angeles Times|date=August 8, 2004|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006090032/http://articles.latimes.com/2004/aug/08/local/me-video8|dead-url=no}}</ref> 范德福德的第二目的是指出主流媒体将会怎样不加批判地接受一部匿名视频。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/5629119/|title=American fakes own decapitation in tape|work=[[MSNBC|MSNBC]]|agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|date=August 7, 2004|accessdate=November 23, 2010|archive-date=2012-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025164245/http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/5629119/|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{le|全球伊斯兰媒体阵线|Global Islamic Media Front (GIMF)}}声称制作了这部视频，但是在被揭穿后将该视频从他们的网站上删除了。<ref>{{cite news|title=American's Iraq 'Beheading' a Hoax|url=http://www.foxnews.com/story/2004/08/08/american-iraq-beheading-hoax/|accessdate=October 3, 2014|agency=Associated Press|publisher=Fox News|date=August 7, 2004|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150413071035/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2004/08/08/american-iraq-beheading-hoax/|archive-date=2015-04-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>该视频也出现在其他激进分子的网站上，也被一些阿拉伯语电视台节目所引用。<ref>{{cite news|title=US man made hoax execution video|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/3544032.stm|accessdate=October 3, 2014|publisher=BBC|date=August 7, 2004|archive-date=2021-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212003025/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/3544032.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Iraq Beheading Video Of US Man A Hoax|url=http://news.sky.com/story/286773/iraq-beheading-video-of-us-man-a-hoax|accessdate=October 3, 2014|publisher=Sky News|date=August 9, 2004|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006112802/http://news.sky.com/story/286773/iraq-beheading-video-of-us-man-a-hoax|dead-url=no}}</ref>

